            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">nephropathy</ENAMEX> in type <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX> and type 2 <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">diabetes</ENAMEX>. Any degree of albuminuria is a risk factor
