            What additional pharmacotherapy should be started at this time?
            The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patient</ENAMEX> has developed neuropathy and erectile dysfunction, both of which are
            complications of <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">diabetes</ENAMEX>. He continues to have suboptimal glycemic control; therefore,
